sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant Post as Post Service
    participant FO as Fan-out Service
    participant PDB as Posts Store
    participant TL as Timeline Cache
    participant Feed as Feed Service
    participant Rank as Ranker

    Note over U,Rank: WRITE PATH (post + hybrid fan-out)
    U->>Post: POST /post
    Post->>PDB: persist post
    PDB-->>Post: post_id
    Post-)FO: enqueue fan-out
    Post-->>U: 200 {post_id}
    alt author followers < 10k (push)
        FO->>FO: load follower list
        loop each follower
            FO->>TL: ZADD timeline (cap 1000)
        end
    else celebrity (>= 10k followers)
        Note over FO: skip push, mark for pull-on-read
    end

    Note over U,Rank: READ PATH (timeline merge)
    U->>Feed: GET /feed
    Feed->>TL: read pre-built timeline (push)
    TL-->>Feed: post_ids
    Feed->>PDB: pull recent celebrity posts
    PDB-->>Feed: celeb posts
    Feed->>Rank: score(candidates)
    Rank-->>Feed: top 50 ranked
    Feed->>PDB: hydrate post details
    PDB-->>Feed: enriched posts
    Feed-->>U: paginated feed
